Language: <F P=105> Romanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] We have received the following communique from the 
Ministry of Foreign Affairs: The Ministry of Foreign Affairs of 
Romania was pleased to learn about the joint declaration of the 
European Union and the Russian Federation addressed to the 
Tiraspol authorities, intended to save the life of Ion Ilascu 
and the urgent transferring of the members of the Ilascu group 
to a legally established court of the Republic of Moldova, which 
can ensure a fair trial, on the basis of internationally 
accepted juridical norms. [passage indistinct] 

